Little known, Wuhan, Wuhan, was one of the top five cities in China's GDP from the end of the Qing Dynasty to the beginning of the reform and opening-up period. After changing open, be affected by policy for a time, be overtaken by coastal area city. Now that Wuhan has taken advantage of its geographical location, it has taken the opportunity of the October 2019 Military World Games to transform the city into a "plastic surgery" . During this period, the whole city of Wuhan was almost surrounded by this green wall, hiding the mission of reviving Wuhan Great Again and the dream of returning to the "new front" .
